<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="84" type="ecology">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="84">Ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="84">Not rare in humid and lowland hill forests, including secondary vegetation. It is also found in shady places in dry forest, especially along riversides.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="84" type="phenology">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="84">Phenology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="84">Flowering from November to January, fruits collected in January and April.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
